## Limitations

The report is based on secondary data sources, which may not capture the latest developments in the field. Additionally, the perspectives discussed are primarily theoretical and may not fully reflect the diversity of educational experiences across different cultural and socio-economic contexts. Further empirical research is needed to explore the nuanced relationship between education and society in various settings.

